      ],
      "source": "https://www.friendsofballpond.com/about-the-pond"
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "text": "A state‑owned boat launch at the southern end lets visitors launch kayaks, canoes, and small rowboats, but motors of any kind are prohibited.",
      "sourceSentenceIds": [
        15,
        16,
        30
      ],
      "sourceLabels": [
