      ],
      "source": "https://www.friendsofballpond.com/about-the-pond"
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "text": "Ball Pond drains east into Ball Pond Brook, a tributary of Candlewood Lake, and its waters are fed entirely by bottom springs and surface runoff.",
      "sourceSentenceIds": [
        27
      ],
      "sourceLabels": [
        "Web source 2"
